Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Former ICE Director Tom Homan: “I’ve worked with six Presidents…I know what policies work. I know what policies don’t. President Trump was a game-changer, and we saved thousands of lives by securing that Southern Border. Biden and Harris took the Most Secure Border in my lifetime, and UNSECURED IT ON PURPOSE.”
